summary: Quiet spiders finally! Reduced foot sound for spiders.
descriptionHtml:
Finally spiders are much quieter!
Annoyed by the excessive loud splish-splash sound for crawling spiders? You don't want them to be totally silent when moving though?
Then this mod is for you!

Mechanical Dwarven spiders sound is not affected.

Language: any.

THIS MOD HAS BEEN ABANDONED
Try instead [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23833/?]SMPC[/url] and SMPC Sound Fixes...
author: Hexaae

files.name: First version
files.changelogHtml: Reduced splish-splash sound for crawling spiders a lot!
